#

Southwestern Chicken Burger

35 min
$12.99
550 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Gluten (if using regular buns)Dairy (from cheese)

Dietary Tags:

Protein-richGluten-free option available

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickEasyGrillComfort Food

Description

A juicy chicken burger with a spicy kick, topped with fresh avocado and zesty chipotle mayo, all served on a soft bun.

Ingredients

  • ground chicken: 1 lb
  • burger buns: 4
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • lettuce: 1 cup
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • pepper jack cheese: 4 slices
  • chipotle mayonnaise: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cumin: 1 tsp
  • paprika: 1 tsp
  • garlic powder: 1/2 tsp
